? 'The process of electrons arriving or leaving is exactly what happens when certain
  combinations of materials are rubbed together: electrons from the atoms of one material
  are forced by the rubbing to leave their respective atoms and transfer over to the
  atoms of the other material.  In other words, electrons comprise the "fluid" hypothesized
  by Benjamin Franklin.'
: {tag: '<para>

    ', xlate: 'El proceso de electrones llegar o salir es exactamente lo que ocurre
